{"tid":2355862,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"曼城報價1500萬英鎊買美斯","createTime":"2021-01-06T11:25:40.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-07T04:56:59.000Z","uid":173952,"like":33,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"9f3b06b1e35e77af2f137c112f181ff936941c6e","tid":2355862,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T11:25:40.000Z","msg":"早排美斯話要同巴塞解約搞到滿城風雨，最終呢位阿根廷球王都係留喺巴塞踢埋今個賽季，但係佢同巴塞嘅合約到明年夏天到期，最近又再有消息話曼城再向球王出手，但出價就相當低。<br />\n巴塞啱啱喺西甲輸畀基達菲，好多人都跌晒眼鏡，更令人懷疑美斯喺球隊嘅存在感，令佢季尾離隊嘅消息再度升溫，<span class=\"red\">據英媒報道，曼城計劃明年1月再次出手，希望可以同美斯傾得掂，但據悉藍月亮只會開出1500萬英鎊嘅轉會費。</span><br />\n知情人透露美斯同巴塞續約嘅機會好微，而《鏡報》報道巴塞主帥朗奴高文已經接受美斯明年離開，仲諗住斟介利物浦嘅韋拿杜姆同埋曼城嘅艾利加西亞，下季嘅巴塞應該會大執位。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08088b3bb9e32d24c2d5a4d0d353e703b232f546","tid":2355862,"uid":209773,"like":18,"dislike":9,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T11:36:29.000Z","msg":"美斯係值咁多啦"},{"pid":"4778d225dd2f3fc569fecfa4c6dcd0f591e7175a","tid":2355862,"uid":14075,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T11:37:34.000Z","msg":"牙朗又贏"},{"pid":"bef83feaab2538babfa7c35873fad1a08dd85c68","tid":2355862,"uid":99700,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T11:39:19.000Z","msg":"正啦 淨半年約仲賣到1500萬鎊"},{"pid":"59d0d2befc8bdb89dfb268553664d345e4df0b07","tid":2355862,"uid":213841,"like":13,"dislike":4,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T11:43:52.000Z","msg":"艾力臣都2700啦 美斯好cheap<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ab11a58c2dbc9f58e20479fbcd09c8b9cef86f1","tid":2355862,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"59d0d2befc8bdb89dfb268553664d345e4df0b07","tid":2355862,"uid":213841,"like":13,"dislike":4,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T11:43:52.000Z","msg":"艾力臣都2700啦 美斯好cheap<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/